===Russian===

==Interjection==
#Either будь здоров(а) (when addressing a single person who is familiar to you; use здоров for males and здорова for females) or будьте здоровы (when addressing multiple people or, more commonly, someone to whom you are being respectful):  literally, the mandate, "Be healthy."  See also [[быть]] and [[здоров]].
#Said to someone who has sneezed to wish them good health.

